William Schaffner oo ka tirsan Jaamacadda Vanderbilt ayaa yiri, "Waxaan u maleynayaa in coronavirus-ka, sababtoo ah wuxuu noqon karaa mid aan la isku halleyn karin, uusan u badneyn sida uu u kala duwanaan karo cudur-darrada waqtiga, oo uu noqon karo mid sanad ka dib.
Awoodda fayraska ayaa ku xiran jirka oo la kulma fayraska iyo isbeddelka.
Calaamadaha COVID-19 waxay noqon karaan kuwo aan caadi ahayn, dadka qaba cudurka ayaa laga yaabaa inaysan calaamado muujin.
Labada xanuun ee ugu badan waa qandho (88%) iyo shubanka sare (68%).
