Sawirada iyo sawirada CT (CT) ee dadka qaba xanuunka waxay ka dhigan tahay in la sameeyo sawir-gacmeedka mugdiga ah ee aan lahayn iftiin badan oo neefsashada ah.
Ururka Radiology ee Talyaaniga ayaa ururinaya macluumaad ka yimid wadamo kala duwan oo ku saabsan sawirada bukaanada la ogaaday inay qabaan cudurka.
Sida cudurrada kale sida adenovirus, sawirada aan la hubin ee PCR-ka ayaa ah kuwo aad u yar oo lagu ogaan karo COVID-19.
Daraasad kale oo lagu sameeyay Shiinaha ayaa isbarbar dhig ku sameysay natiijooyinka CT-ga wadnaha iyo PCR waxayna muujisay in xitaa haddii cudurku yahay mid aan la ogaan karin, uu yahay mid deg deg ah oo la taaban karo, taas oo muujineysa faa'iidada ay u leedahay qalab baaritaan oo ku saabsan aagagga cudurka.
Nidaamyada loo yaqaan 'convolutional neural networks' ayaa loo sameeyay si loo muujiyo sawirada fayraska labadaba raadiyaha iyo CT.
