Daboolka waxaa lagu nadiifin karaa habab kala duwan (hal daqiiqo gudahood marka la mariyo qalabka saxan ee saxanka cuntada), sida 62-72% ethanol, 50100% isopropanol, 0.1% sodium hypochlorite, 0.5% hydrogen peroxide, iyo 0.27.5% povidone-iodine.
Qaababka kale sida benzalkonium chloride iyo chrohexidine gluconate, ma aha kuwo aad u xoog badan.
CDC waxay ku talineysaa in haddii qof qaba COVID uu ku dhaco ama uu ku dhaco meel kale sida goobta shaqada ama isbitaalka, dhammaan goobaha sida xafiisyada, furayaasha, bakhaarada, amarrada la qaybiyo, kaararka aqoonsiga muuqaalka, kaararka diiwaangelinta amarka, telecommands, iyo kaararka ATM ee uu isticmaalo qofka uu xanuunka qaba waa in la nadiifiyaa.
