Maaskaro wajiga ah ayaa lagula talinayaa dadka qaba cudurka, maadaama xirashada maaskaro wajiga ah ay yareyn karto neefsashada iyo ka fogaanshaha neefsashada, hadalka, qufaca, ama neefta.
WHO waxay soo saartay macluumaad ku saabsan goorta iyo sida loo xirto maaskaro.
Sida laga soo xigtay Stephen Griffin, oo ah borofisar ku takhasusay fayraska ee Jaamacadda Leeds, "Garabka wajiga ayaa laga yaabaa inuu yareeyo fursadda dadka ay ku taabtaan wajiga, taas oo ah habka ugu horeeya ee loo qaadi karo cudurka iyada oo aan si fiican loo dhaqin".Gabka wajiga ayaa sidoo kale lagula talinayaa daryeelayaasha dadka qaba cudurka.
WHO waxay ku talineysaa in la xirto maaskaro dadka aan cudurka qabin oo keliya marka ay suurtagal tahay in la ogaado cudurka, sida kuwa daryeela qof qaba COVID-19, ama marka la ogaado in xirashada maaskaro ay ka horjoogsan karto dadka inay taabtaan wajiga.
Wadamada badankood waxay bilaabeen inay xirtaan dharka indhaha ee indhaha.
