Ilaa hadda, ma jiraan wax caddayn ah oo muujinaya in isticmaalka antiseptics ama sunta sunta ay dooranayaan noocyada ugu adag ee antibiyootikada.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, saabuunta antibacterial waxay leeyihiin waxyaabo ka hortagga bakteeriyada sida triclosan, oo leh tiro badan oo ah waxyaabaha sunta lagu dilo.
Sidoo kale, inkasta oo unugyada anti-bakteeriyada ay ka difaacaan saabuunta difaacaya bakteeriyada, ma aha mid aad u xoog badan sida ku xusan astaamaha.
Si loo kordhiyo surfactants iyo waxyaabaha ka hortagga jirka, isku darka waxyaabaha waxaa laga yaabaa inay ku jiraan acids (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid) sida PH inhibitor, benzoic acid oo dilaya fayraska iyo waxyaabaha ka hortagga jirka (aloe vera, fitamiin, menthol, daawooyinka daawooyinka). Daraasado lagu sameeyay Jaamacadda Oregon School of Public Health ayaa lagu ogaaday in saabuunta aan la isticmaalin ay ka dhigan tahay mid ka mid ah saabuunta la isticmaalo ee ay ku jiraan triclosan si loo yareeyo cudurada iyo in laga saaro bakteeriyada gacmaha.
