ACE waxay u bedeshaa angiotensin I hormoon ahaan iyadoo la adeegsanayo angiotensin II.
ACE2 sidoo kale waxay u bedeshaa amino acid-ka carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) oo ay ku jirto angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH) oo ah vasodilator.
