Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 wuxuu u adeegaa sida albaabka kaliya ee unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada, sida HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska sababa SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska sababa COVID-19).
